(71995, 2431, 71962, 'Basharat', 60, '', 1258615983, 'As a member of the Defence Industry, i have some experience with Armored vehicles.  If you are importing kits to locally armor vehicles, in addition to your import license and trade license etc. you need an NOC from the MOI and the Home Dept of the province you are operating in.  and you are only authorized to sell armored vehicles to a customer who has an NOC from the MOI and the Home Dept of the province where the vehicle will be used (even if he is going to use it in another province once in 10 years he needs an NOC from the Home Dept of that province as well).  You need these NOCs before the material or finished product can even enter the country.   \n\nIt upsets me a great deal when people do not follow the law and as a result give a bad name to a larger group.', 0, 1, '58.181.102.50', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 3199, 81097),
