(73058, 54, 399, 'Basharat', 60, '', 1259043620, '@All\n\nThe first question you ask your self should be what specific activity has the section 144 been placed on.  is it on carrying, is it on display?  \n\n1.  If it is section 144 on the display of Arms then you can not show your weapon but can carry it in a concealed manner.  \n2.  If it is section 144 on carrying a weapon or going armed then you can not conceal carry a weapon on your person but you can keep it in your car.  \n3.  if it is section 144 on transportation then you can not have the weapon in your car.  \n\nIt is important to understand which activity has been restricted under the 144 in place.', 0, 1, '58.181.102.27', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 73, 82231),
