(77811, 2624, 77802, 'Glockcohlic', 1253, '', 1260794788, '[b]Walther P22 Specifications & Features:[/b]\n\n\n[b]- Internal trigger lock\n- Loaded chamber indicator\n- Magazine disconnect\n- Ambidextrous safety and ambidextrous magazine release\n- Lanyard loop, \n- 2 magazines.\n- Easily interchangeable barrels 3.4" and 5" target.\n- Light polymer frame.\n- Interchangeable rear grip panel to fit different size hands\n- Adjustable 3-Dot rear sight and interchangeable front sights.\n- Firing pin safety.[/b]\n\n[b]Specifications:[/b]\n\n[b]- Caliber: 22LR\n- Magazine Capacity: 10 Rounds \n- Action: Traditional Double Action\n- Weight: 19.6 oz.\n- Barrel \n- Length: 3.4"\n- Overall Length: 6.26"\n- Width: 1.14"\n- Height: 4.49"\n- Grips: Interchangeable Back Straps\n- Front Sight: Interchangeable White 2-Dot\n- Rear Sight: Adjustable White Dot\n- Safety: Magazine Disconnect, Firing Pin Safety, Loaded Chamber Indicator[/b]', 0, 1, '203.215.36.58', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 3459, 87541),
(77812, 2624, 77802, 'Glockcohlic', 1253, '', 1260795874, '[b]Glock 34, Specifications & Features:[/b]\n\nThe Glock 34 as you know is a competition version of the Glock 17. It is similar to its predecessor, the now-discontinued Glock 17L, but with a slightly shorter slide and barrel. It was developed and produced in 1998, and compared to the Glock 17, features a 21 mm (0.8 in) longer barrel and slide. It also has an extended magazine release, extended slide stop lever, 4.5 lbs trigger pull, and an adjustable rear sight. The top of the slide is milled out, creating a hole designed to reduce front-end muzzle weight to better balance the pistol.\n\n[b]	Caliber: 9x19 mm\n	Action: Safe Action (constant double action mode)\n	Overall length (slide): 8.15 in. (207 mm)\n	Height, including magazine: 5.43 in. (138 mm)\n	Width: 1.18 in. (30 mm)\n	Barrel length: 5.32 in. (135 mm)\n	Sight radius: 7.32 in. (186 mm)\n	Rifling: Hexagonal profile: with right-hand twist of one turn in 9.84 in. (250 mm)\n	Weight without magazine: 22.92 oz. (650 g)\n	Weight, empty magazine: 2.75 oz. (78 g)\n	Weight, full magazine: ~9.87 oz. (~280 g)\n	Magazine capacity: 17 rounds\n	Standard trigger pull: ~4.5 lbs. (~2.0 kg)\n	Trigger pull length: 0.5 in. (12.5 mm)\n	Number of safeties: 3[/b]', 0, 1, '203.215.36.58', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 3459, 87542),
